.SH NAME
CWE\-22 \- Improper Limitation of a Pathname to a Restricted Directory (Path Traversal)
.SH RANK
2025 CWE Top 25 rank: \fB#6\fR (2024 rank: 5).
.SH CLASSIFICATION
Class: Injection / File System.
.SH DESCRIPTION
User input builds a file path without neutralising sequences such as "../" that resolve outside the intended directory, letting an attacker read or write files anywhere the process can reach.
.SH MITIGATION
Resolve to a canonical absolute path and verify it remains within the intended base directory before opening. Prefer allow\-listing known file identifiers over accepting raw paths.
